<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ861202-0151 </DOCNO><HL> Dividend News:Pier 1 Imports Inc.</HL><DD> 12/02/86</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> PIRDIVIDENDS (DIV) </IN><TEXT>   PIER 1 IMPORTS INC. said its board declared a 4-for-3 stock split and boosted its dividend on an annual basis. The company, which currently pays a semiannual dividend of two cents a pre-split share, said it will begin paying a quarterly dividend of two cents a post-split share. Pier 1 said the split is payable Jan. 13 to stock of record Dec. 16, and its dividend is payable Feb. 27 to stock of record Feb. 13. The Fort Worth, Texas-based specialty retailer of home furnishings and related items said it currently has 14,078,066 common shares outstanding. </TEXT></DOC>